And, behold, there came a leper and worshipped him, saying, Lord, if thou wilt, thou canst make me clean.","year":31},{"id":"recS4MYpzoV2cfbyZ","ref":"Matt.8.3","text":"And Jesus put forth his hand, and touched him, saying, I will; be thou clean. And immediately his leprosy was cleansed.","year":31},{"id":"recvVuTMhNAsksg1H","ref":"Matt.8.4","text":"And Jesus saith unto him, See thou tell no man; but go thy way, shew thyself to the priest, and offer the gift that Moses commanded, for a testimony unto them.","year":31},{"id":"recFmipbUXMNcCnJ5","ref":"Matt.8.5","text":"And when Jesus was entered into Capernaum, there came unto him a centurion, beseeching him,","year":31},{"id":"recH75GnLQRJznrNW","ref":"Matt.8.6","text":"And saying, Lord, my servant lieth at home sick of the palsy, grievously tormented.","year":31},{"id":"rec3gdpUe7hxeNq8e","ref":"Matt.8.7","text":"And Jesus saith unto him, I will come and heal him.","year":31},{"id":"rec45AIVoXdvuOpyX","ref":"Matt.8.8","text":"The centurion answered and said, Lord, I am not worthy that thou shouldest come under my roof: but speak the word only, and my servant shall be healed.","year":31}]}
